    "As shown in Table4, the gain over CTR_BBM (+0.6pp in AUC) demonstrates that replacing black-box prompt summaries with white-box, attention-guided representations better captures item semantics, leading to more accurate user interest modeling.ModelAUC ↑ LogLoss ↓CTR_BBM0.65800.0234 CTR_FITRep 0.66400.0215 Table 5:5Online A/B testing results on Meituan's advertising system.We identify the local structural collapse problem in existing blackbox multimodal representations, which leads to false-positive duplicates and degraded user experience.",
    "To address this, we propose FITRep, a white-box, attention-guided framework inspired by FIT that enables fine-grained, interpretable item representation through concept-hierarchical extraction, structure-preserving dimensionality reduction, and scalable indexing."
